  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.1.0-alpha01\" data-text=\"Version 1.1.0-alpha01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.1.0-alpha01</h3>\n<p>December 3, 2018</p>\n<p><strong>New features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Support tinting using <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ColorStateLists</code> defined with theme attrs in <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">VectorDrawableCompat</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bug fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed bug in rendering <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">VectorDrawables</code> with gradients (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/platform/frameworks/support/+/790377/\">aosp/790377</a>)</li>\n<li>Fixed <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">getColorFilter()</code> that returned null even when it was set (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/platform/frameworks/support/+/762198/\">aosp/762198</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_100_5\" data-text=\"Version 1.0.0\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.0.0</h2>",
  "commitsUrl": "https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/platform/frameworks/support/+/790377/"
}